        <updateDate>2023-10-23T15:07:36Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Speech Privacy Act of 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits, with certain exceptions, any entity of the federal government from collecting or requiring the submission of information on the identification of any donor to a tax-exempt organization. It also prohibits an entity from disclosing to the public information identifying a donor.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
